    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4655647>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Megaraphidia klondika sp. nov., specimen SRUI99-71-63. A, part; B, counterpart; C, drawing of the hind wing venation. Scale bar = 3 mm (all to scale)." ;
